Connor Trinneer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connor_Trinneer 0 Connor Trinneer (born March 19, 1969) is an American film, stage, and television actor. He is best known for his role as Charles "Trip" Tucker III on Star Trek: Enterprise, as Michael on the series Stargate Atlantis, and as Professor Moynihan on the web series Guilty Party.
